2026-05-16T03:04:22.0698546Z 228            and the extra is missing, it NPEs on
2026-05-16T03:04:22.0699528Z 229            PendingIntent.getIntentSender(). noHistory + excludeFromRecents
2026-05-16T03:04:22.0700300Z 230            finishes the activity as soon as it leaves the foreground so it
